    "description": "<p>Casa Raudha Ltd is a dedicated social service organization focused on supporting survivors of domestic violence. Initially established to provide shelter for those in crisis, Casa Raudha has since broadened its services to include community outreach, awareness programs, and initiatives aimed at fostering family resilience. The organization is committed to building a society free from domestic violence by helping families stay united in a healthy and conducive home environment.</p>",
